(ies qrHW ijs mnu`K dy AMdr auh) lukvIN (r`bI jIvn dI) rO prgt huMdI hY (Bwv, ijs nUM auh Awpxy AMg-sMg qy sB ivc ivAwpk id`s pYNdw hY),
hy nwnk! auh mnu`K aus s`cy pRBU (dy nwm-rUp saudy) dI kdr smJ lYNdw hY ]53]
jy Afolqw ivc rih ky (pRBU nUM) imlIey qW (pUrn) suK huMdw hY[
jo mnu`K gurU dy hukm ivc qurdw hY auh sucyq rihMdw hY (mwieAw dI) nINdr ivc nhIN sauNdw[
prmwqmw dI is&q-swlwh dI bwxI aus nUM byAMq pRBU ivc itkweI r`KdI hY[
(ies bwxI nUM) aucwr aucwr ky gurmuK haumY qoN suqMqr ho jWdw hY qy (hornW nUM) ies Sbd dI rwhIN mukq krWdw hY[
ijn@W gurU dI is`iKAw igRhx kIqI hY auh s`cy pRBU ivc rMgy gey hn[
hy nwnk! Awpw-Bwv imtw ky auhnW dw myl (pRBU nwl) ho jWdw hY, (mn dI) Btkxw imt jWdI hY ]54]
(pRSn:) ieh g`l iks QW qy ho skdI hY ik mnu`K AwpxI BYVI m`q dUr kr ley?
mnu`K ikauN AslIAq nhIN smJdw qy duKI huMdw hY,
jm dy dr qy b`Dy hoey dI koeI shYqw nhIN kr skdw,
siqgurU dy Sbd qoN ibnw ies dI ikqy ie`zq nhIN, ieqbwr nhIN (Bwv, gurU dy Sbd Anuswr nwh qurn krky mnu`K lokW ivc ie`zq ieqbwr gvw lYNdw hY, dunIAw dIAW mOjW ivc PisAw hox krky mOq qoN BI hr vyly frdw hY ieho ijhIAw s`tW sdw KWdw rihMdw hY, duKI rihMdw hY, iPr BI AslIAq nUM smJdw nhIN[ ieh ikauN?)[
ieh ikvyN smJy qy ('du`qr swgr' dy) pwrly kMFy l`gy?
hy nwnk! mnmuK mUrK smJdw nhIN ]55]
(au~qr:) siqgurU dw Sbd vIcwirAW BYVI mq dUr huMdI hY[
jdoN gurU iml pYNdw hY, qdoN ies BYVI mq qoN ^lwsI dw rwh l`B pYNdw hY[
(pr) jo mnu`K mn dy ip`Cy qurdw hY auh AslIAq nhIN pCwxdw, (ivkwrW ivc) sVdw rihMdw hY,
durm`q dy kwrn (pRBU qoN) ivCuV ky duKI huMdw hY[
jo mnu`K gurU dw hukm mMndw hY, aus ivc swry gux Aw jWdy hn, aus nUM swrI sUJ pRwpq ho jWdI hY[
hy nwnk!auh pRBU dI hzUrI ivc Awdr pWdw hY ]56]
ijs mnu`K ny s`cw saudw nwm-Dn K`itAw hY,
auh Awp ('du`qr swgr' qoN) qrdw hY qy (hornW nUM) qwrdw hY[
Afol AvsQw ivc msq rih ky AslIAq nUM smJdw hY qy Awdr pWdw hY,
Ajyhy mnu`K dw koeI mu`l nhIN pw skdw[
auh ij`Dr q`kdw hY auDr pRBU hI pRBU aus nUM ivAwpk id`sdw hY
hy nwnk! s`cy dI rzw ivc rih ky auh mnu`K ('duqr swgr' qoN) pwr lMG jWdw hY ]57]
(pRSn:) ijs Sbd dI rwhIN sMswr-smuMdr qrIdw hY aus Sbd dw itkwxw ik`Qy ikhw jw skdw hY?
'pRwx' (Bwv suAws) nUM ds-auNgl-pRmwx khIdw hY d`so, ies dw kIh Awsrw hY?
(jo jIvwqmw ies srIr ivc) boldw qy klol krdw hY, auh sdw leI ikvyN Afol ho skdw hY qy ikvyN aus pRBU nUM vyKy ijs dw koeI ^ws ichn c`kR nhIN[
nwnk kihMdw hY (jogIAW ny pu`iCAw) hy suAwmI! s`cy pRBU dI g`l sux ky mnu`K Awpxy mn nUM ikvyN sum`qy lw skdw hY?
(au~qr:) jo mnu`K gurU dy hukm ivc qurdw hY, gurU Sbd dI rwhIN aus dI ilv s`cy pRBU ivc l`g jWdI hY, (qy, pRBU) myhr dI nzr kr ky aus nUM Awpxy ivc joV lYNdw hY,
(ikauNik) pRBU (aus dy idl dI) Awp hI jwxdw hY, Awp hI pCwxdw hY[ (ies qrHW) au~cI iksmq krky (gurmuiK mnu`K pRBU ivc) itikAw rihMdw hY ]58]
(ijs 'Sbd' dI rwhIN "du`qr swgr" qrIdw hY) aus 'Sbd' nUM ie`k-rs QW (imilAw hoieAw) hY (Bwv, auh Sbd hr QW BrpUr hY), 'Sbd' Al`K (pRBU dw rUp) hY, mYN ijDr vyKdw hW auh Sbd hI Sbd hY[
ijvyN APur pRBU dw vws (hr QW) hY iqvyN 'Sbd' dw vws (hr QW) hY[ 'Sbd' auhI hY jo sMpUrx s`iqAw-DwrI (pRBU) hY (Bwv 'pRBU' qy pRBU dI is&q dw 'Sbd' ie`k hI hn)[
ijs mnu`K auqy pRBU myhr dI nzr krdw hY, aus dy ihrdy ivc ieh 'Sbd' v`sdw hY, auh mnu`K ihrdy ivcoN Btkxw dUr kr lYNdw hY,
aus dw qn qy aus dw mn qy aus dI bwxI pivqR ho jWdy hn[ pRBU dw nwm hI auh mnu`K Awpxy mn ivc vsweI r`Kdw hY[
siqgur dy 'Sbd' dI rwhIN sMswr-smuMdr qrIdw hY[ (jo qirAw hY auh) ieQy auQy (lok prlok ivc hr QW) ie`k pRBU nUM ivAwpk jwxdw hY[
hy nwnk! jo mnu`K ies 'Sbd' nUM pCwx lYNdw hY 'Sbd' nwl fUMGI sWJ pw lYNdw hY aus auqy mwieAw dw pRBwv nhIN rihMdw qy aus dw Awpxw v`Krw ichn qy vrn nhIN rih jWdw (Bwv, aus dw v`Krw-pn imt jWdw hY, aus dy AMdroN myr-qyr dUr ho jWdI hY) ]59]
(au~qr:) hy jogI! ds-auNgl-pRmwx pRwxW dI ^urwk APur s`cw pRBU hY (Bwv, suAws suAws pRBU dw nwm hI jpxw hY, pRBU dw nwm hI pRwxW dw Awsrw hY)[
jo mnu`K gurU dy hukm ivc qur ky (suAws suAws pRBU dw nwm) jpdw hY, auh AslIAq (Bwv, jgq dw mUl) hwsl kr lYNdw hY, auh Al`K qy Apwr pRBU nUM pCwx lYNdw hY (pRBU nwl fUMGI sWJ pw lYNdw hY)[
jdoN mnu`K gurU dw Sbd ihrdy ivc vsWdw hY (Sbd dI brkiq nwl mwieAw dw) qRY-guxI pRBwv imtw lYNdw hY, qW aus dy mn ivcoN AhMkwr nws ho jWdw hY[
(ies qrHW) jdoN auh Awpxy AMdr qy bwhr (jgq ivc) ie`k pRBU nUM hI vyKdw hY, qW aus dw ipAwr pRBU dy nwm ivc bx jWdw hY[
hy nwnk! jdoN Al`K pRBU Awpxw Awp lKWdw hY (Awpxy srUp dI smJ b^Sdw hY), qdoN gurmuK ieVw ipMgulw suKmnw nUM smJ lYNdw hY,
(Bwv, gurmuiK nUM ieh smJ Aw jWdI hY ik) sdw kwiem rihx vwlw pRBU ieVw ipMgulw suKmnw dy A`iBAws qoN auqWh hY, aus ivc qW siqgurU dy Sbd dI rwhIN (hI) smweIdw hY ]60]
(pRSn:) mn dw Awsrw pRwx khIdy hn, pRwx ikQoN ^urwk lYNdy hn? (Bwv, pRwxW dw Awsrw kOx hY?)
hy jogI! igAwn dI pRwpqI dw kyhVw swDn hY? jog-swDnW ivc pu`gy hoey jogI nUM kIh pRwpq ho jWdw hY?
